  "body": "We are using `\"no-return-wait\": \"error\"`, but it would've be better to do the opposite and to actually enforce `return await` everywhere, so that we have better async stack traces. See [this comment](https://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/pull/1587#discussion_r658937143).\r\n\r\nLinks:\r\n\r\n- [`no-return-await`](https://eslint.org/docs/rules/no-return-await)\r\n- [`@typescript-eslint/return-await`](https://github.com/typescript-eslint/typescript-eslint/blob/master/packages/eslint-plugin/docs/rules/return-await.md)",
